Package cfa.vo.sedlib.io

Interface Summary
ISedDeserializer Defines management of reading Sed objects from files and streams.
ISedSerializer Defines management of writing Sed objects to file and streams.
 

Class Summary
AbstractWriter<T> Interface for writing wrapped objects to files, streams.
FitsDeserializer Deserializes FITS formatted data to Sed objects.
FitsMapper Maps Sed objects to Fits objects
FitsSerializer Serializes a Sed object to a Fits formatted file.
IOConstants Defines constant values used throughout the IO portion of the library.
SedIOFactory A factory for retrieving an appropriate SED library deserializer and serializer.
SedMapper Defines management of updating Sed objects from other well defined objects.
VOTableDeserializer Deserializes VOTable formatted data to Sed objects.
VOTableMapper Maps Sed objects to VOTable objects
VOTableObject Stores VOTable data including a VOElement and a list of star tables.
VOTableSerializer Serializes a Sed object to a VOTable formatted file.
 

Enum Summary
SedFormat Defines (de)serialization formats supported by the SED Library
